      • char2LongEntrySet

        public ObjectSortedSet<Char2LongMap.Entry> char2LongEntrySet()
        Description copied from interface: Char2LongMap
        Returns a type-specific set view of the mappings contained in this map.

        This method is necessary because there is no inheritance along type parameters: it is thus impossible to strengthen Char2LongMap.entrySet() so that it returns an ObjectSet of type-specific entries (the latter makes it possible to access keys and values with type-specific methods).

        Specified by:
        char2LongEntrySet in interface Char2LongMap
        Specified by:
